{"tid":445782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（戒丁ReaLife）兩千人Telegram群","createTime":"2017-10-23T16:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T15:08:53.000Z","uid":35484,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5f4cf076492f22521b3d8cfdab48c0451f79fb","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"兩千人Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e14447ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram：siudontleave<br />\nFACEBOOK專頁：ReaLife<br />\nReaLife論壇 ：<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=be961fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n<br />\n香港反色情組織 ReaLife 宣傳片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M0YrgzJZRMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM0YrgzJZRMU&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=07c84d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M0YrgzJZRMU</a>"},{"pid":"09d23acbdd5ff617d40f385885f4f8f476cbf617","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞，但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將戒為良藥睇一次"},{"pid":"066451d4fa0478c26de0888dcc161154923d87c9","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"（必睇！）秦東魁老師講解傳統文化<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA%2Fvideos&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=99f05fd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA/videos</a><br />\n可以由邪淫的25種果報開始睇起<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLyVAEphpUDM&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=63750af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LyVAEphpUDM</a>"},{"pid":"b9a173ce7ddecdbeb1923775e73a7fd585e5c081","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"假設心魔等級100，你定力等級只有15，你怎麼能和心魔抗衡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想戒Ｊ成功就睇哂《戒為良藥》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=eUFkIerDo0dRD2pyEi%2BQ6U%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2abfc4b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"483f913e4578c778fbda400a810dadbdb1dfb08d","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"你若盛開，蝴蝶自來。當你每晚在黑暗的角落裡沉迷於黃片、自慰的時候，你可知？這些負能量已經遮掩了你/妳生命的芬芳，讓您身心俱損，病苦連連，時乖運拙，潦倒一生，讓我們戒邪婬，行孝道，恢複本來的純淨與快樂！讓他/她在茫茫人海中一眼看到妳/你！看到那個光芒四射、氣場強大的您！"},{"pid":"41bd43d5e1f322f3fc137e27468cbf048b5b94bf","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T04:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdfa1362a9d6d26c4346f4736e5d2711c07191a","tid":445782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/